      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Great opportunity to own a reliable, well-maintained vehicle! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 This car is in good condition \u2014 it presents nicely with a clean exterior that shows only minor signs of normal use, and the interior is tidy and comfortable. Mechanically, it's running well and ready for daily driving without any major concerns. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's a solid, dependable choice at an honest price. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
