      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and every aspect of it lives up to that designation. The exterior paint is flawless \u2014 a deep, rich gloss with zero scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and all trim pieces, moldings, and chrome accents are pristine. The interior is equally immaculate: seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard show no signs of wear, fading, or staining whatsoever. All mechanical systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, suspension, and electronics \u2014 function perfectly, with no warning lights, unusual noises, or deferred maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that genuinely looks and drives as though it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely transparent with all potential buyers. The car has significant wear and issues that should be carefully considered before purchase \u2014 these include visible body damage such as dents, scratches, and possible rust, as well as interior wear that is well beyond cosmetic. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and will likely require repairs to bring it up to reliable daily-driver status; we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. This listing is best suited for buyers who are experienced with project vehicles, looking for parts, or have the mechanical knowledge and budget to invest in repairs. There is no attempt to hide the car's shortcomings \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we'd rather you walk away informed than disappointed.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car purchase. The exterior presents nicely for its age \u2014 you'll find only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal everyday use, with no significant dents or rust to speak of. The paint retains a good shine overall. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable; the upholstery shows moderate use but no major tears, stains, or damage, and all interior controls and features function as intended. Mechanically, this car is in solid shape \u2014 the engine starts reliably, runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts without issue. Brakes, suspension, and steering all feel responsive and appropriate for a vehicle of this age and mileage. We recommend a pre-purchase inspection, as we always do, but buyers should feel confident that this is a dependable vehicle ready for daily driving without immediate major repairs anticipated.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
